arts.ttl: FC Augsburg vs. VfL Wolfsburg preview: Both sides desperate for 3 points before break
arts.sum: FC Augsburg (1-0-4, 16th) host VfL Wolfsburg (1-2-2, 12th) at the WWK-Arena in the sixth matchweek of the 2025/26 Bundesliga season (Saturday, 15.30 CET). Both teams have failed to win any of their last three matches.
